f0e630c33a8e7f","tid":964063,"uid":26601,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T07:51:58.000Z","msg":"人類歷史就係因為有卡特呢類仆街先會咁高重覆性<br />\n成日行綏靖政策，養到d 極權政府肚滿腸肥遺禍人間<br />\n呢d 民主國家既元首任內如果縱容同向極權靠攏既應該一律捉去海牙法庭審，charge 佢地干犯反人類罪，屌晒你地仆街老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8b45e2d48c19e786f78812758901c658b443c44","tid":964063,"uid":35410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T08:56:50.000Z","msg":"早撚D死啦仆街<br />\n<br />\n冚家產，唔死都唔好咁多嘢講"},{"pid":"31b5587664aeb98a7813339a831a8d311be56618","tid":964063,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T09:24:24.000Z","msg":"呢個美國總統出名廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891af175f6912189994e24f9dab9d90f029eb9c0","tid":964063,"uid":219614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T09:27:56.000Z","msg":"人老真係會退化"},{"pid":"29c782e4bdd39a45c0d7b3bdbfc4fee1dd39e9bc","tid":964063,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T09:29:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"183b9526e36889ae8d506f835c3245239401162f","tid":964063,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T09:30:43.000Z","msg":"嘩你老母臭閪<br />\n開頭以為防止冷戰既做法係盡快令中共倒台實行民主化<br />\n原來係無視放任所有中共既仆街野<br />\n格硬去化解爭議去換取所謂既和平<br />\n<br />\n左膠思想真係好撚恐怖<br />\n應該拉埋連同德國左膠默閪爾一齊槍決"},{"pid":"c96d3b08f3a7b9dbf8ad8d20ba7f7097f53a5226","tid":964063,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T09:33:55.000Z","msg":"Vince Carter我就識"}]}